Text:
@mt_phil

IMO this is an "OK" rip.  The picture and sound are fine and there are no glitches or synch issues.

However, IMO, when they compressed it it dropped too many frames and its kind of noticable.  I had to fiddle with VLan to get it a bit smoother. Being an action movie I want really smooth vid. I generally go with  the 720 because they usually arent as compressed and run smoother but thought for this film I would try 1080.
